@GPhilo: Have you tried to blacklist IsVariableInitialized with the --variable_names_blacklist argument?
I had the same issue with my graph, which were solved by blacklisting the variables.
The problematic variables were used in model to transfer the states of rnn cells from one iteration to another, these really had to remain variables and should not have been converted to constants.

